### Update Book 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code (2nd Edition)",
  "author": "Robert C. Martin",
  "genre": "Programming",
  "publicationYear": 2025,
  "available": false,
  "borrowedStatus": false
}

